snippet.title: Dance With Ego — Honkai Impact 3rd New Battlesuit Herrscher of Human: Ego Trailer!
snippet.description:
"What starts with me also ends with me." When the girl as gorgeous as dancing petals appears, will you dance with her?

Let's go to the banquet together and delve into the "ego" named Elysia.
